Your mother sucks cocks in hell
{{pixplz}}

'''Your mother sucks cocks in hell''' is an unfunny and overused insult/joke/"meme" used mostly by retards and alike to sound more fucking serious.

==Origin of meme==
Your mother sucks cocks in Hell originated from "the Exorcists (1973) where the possessed girl and the Exorcist, Father Damien Karras had the following conversation:


'''Demon''': What an excellent day for an exorcism.

'''Father Damien Karras''': You would like that?

'''Demon''': Intensely.

'''Father Damien Karras''': But wouldn't that drive you out of Regan?

'''Demon''': It would bring us together.

'''Father Damien Karras''': You and Regan?

'''Demon''': You and us.

'''Demon''': I'm not Regan.

'''Father Damien Karras''': Well, then let's introduce ourselves. I'm Damien Karras.

'''Demon''': And I'm the Devil. Now kindly undo these straps.

'''Father Damien Karras''': If you're the Devil, why not make the straps disappear?

'''Demon''': That's much too vulgar a display of power, Karras.

'''Demon''': Your mother's in here, Karras. Would you like to leave a message? I'll see that she gets it.

'''Demon''': Your mother sucks cocks in Hell, Karras, you faithless slime.


==New meme is born==
[[File:Imagesyourmomsuckscocsinhell.jpg|left]]
[[File:Satanic-wolf-YOUR-MOTHER-SUCKS-COCKS-IN-HELL.jpg|thumb|typical unfunny attempt to quote the Exorcist]]
[[File:YOUR-MOTHER-SUCKS-COCKS-IN-HELL.jpg|thumb|Arnold knows what [[you|your]] mother does there]]

For the grief of us all, the [[13-year-old boys]] found this line hilarious and soon quoted it to death in various forums and chats, thus many unfunny "Your mother sucks cocks in Hell" jokes were born.

This "meme" is mainly used by [[13-year-old boys]] and other retards, when trying to be funny and "witty".
Mostly used as a response [[for great justice]], when someone is insultin you for something stupid and retarted you have done.

Example of possible situation:
13-year old Johnny has done something really retarted, like sticking his little weener in a bottle at school WC in hopes of great satisfstion and his pen0r gets stuck in it. Then his friend happens to arrive at the scene and see the embarrassing situation and starts laughing and making fun of little Johnny. and pissed of Johnny responses:
"oh yeah? well your mother sucks cocks...IN HELL!!"

NOTE: this "meme" is not funny, it has never been funny and it propably never will. Avoid using this "meme" at all costs.


